      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RITZA TEARS (2) goes very well this course and distance starting 11 times for six wins and three minors. Comes off a (29.47) win last time, scoring by 2.5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 520m at this track. Expected to go close. DANNY SNITCH (1) was strongly supported last start but missed the frame when fourth (26.54), beaten 5.5 lengths. Has never missed the frame from four starts from this draw, including a win. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. RITZA LAW (8) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with three wins and a placing from five tries. Recorded a 1.3 lengths win (29.54) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Looks one of the chances. TAKE A BREAK (3) comes off a (29.63) win last time, scoring by 2 lengths in a Grade 5 over 520m at this track. Yet to taste defeat in two runs from this draw.",
